dc_title_s: Line Features of the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment, California, 1997-1998
dc_description_s: This polygon layer is a merged shapefile of all line features created for the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment in 1998. Line features within this file include the assessment boundary, building outlines, paved roads, unpaved roads and trails. This shapefile was created for the purposes of providing one GIS layer that describes the line features assessed during the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment. These features are intended for the purposes of mapping and assessment.
